{"tid":2196889,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國谷數碼人幣 勢在港推行","createTime":"2020-09-10T08:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T09:04:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f309b11e722837edf36ee5dfc8b81a627d5f39b8","tid":2196889,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200910/OMSYFSDIYFE6FB6WBI5PUZY4GI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200910%2FOMSYFSDIYFE6FB6WBI5PUZY4GI%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE80BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=0d406957\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200910%2FOMSYFSDIYFE6FB6WBI5PUZY4GI%2F&h=39a8462f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200910/OMSYFSDIYFE6FB6WBI5PUZY4GI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國谷數碼人幣 勢在港推行<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共以異乎尋常速度開發數碼貨幣（DCEP，Digital Currency Electronic Payment），目前已要求內地銀行及科技公司試行，似乎想在國際支付科技標準上搶奪話語權，而相關產品已表明將來會在「粵港澳大灣區」推廣，香港料不會缺席。分析認為，數碼人民幣相關交易藏有使用者足迹，被中共監控風險高，是為擴大使用範疇的一大挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。中國過去十年移動支付迅速增長，2018年交易總額達5萬億人民幣，約佔所有支付的80%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x2lZbn4W3F0cy5RrlA9286c8cyw=/943x648/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FFNF4LRPXFDZTKHQTHJXPJB7FI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx2lZbn4W3F0cy5RrlA9286c8cyw%3D%2F943x648%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFFNF4LRPXFDZTKHQTHJXPJB7FI.jpg&h=9f968312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府可掌握交易及流向<br />\n<br />\n第二，數碼人幣可被中共政府掌握交易及流向，有。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n若要數最大的誘因，外界料中共意在挑戰美元的霸權地位。市場一直憂慮，美國有機會限制中港使用SWIFT（環球銀行金融電信協會）系統進行美元清算，作為金融武器之一。數碼人幣推出後，意味人民幣跨境交易可繞過SWIFT直接進行。建銀國際報告亦認同，建立數字化跨境支付清算和信息網絡，是應對美國制裁的方法之一。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。反而數碼人幣可追蹤資金流向，引起歐洲央行等爭議，關注用戶私隱度。。。。。"},{"pid":"7d7366c8139840453d2f05b9e96b1996df7bc1de","tid":2196889,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"美國再唔打柒大陸<br />\n仲9下9下<br />\n遲早俾大陸食撚埋"},{"pid":"7a8a7a725b0f7ac26549500bba18279178c40202","tid":2196889,"uid":322130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"大陸班友點敢再投資，隨時又割9菜"},{"pid":"2421a181ec817151653eceba8428fb0b41d9a9ba","tid":2196889,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"1984"},{"pid":"97fffccdc1e5f10b1e06c347d8538a1a765647a4","tid":2196889,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194107</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}